openaiSpec.name: recall_chat_memory

query.description: The query representing the current chat context or specific information you need to recall from past conversations.

openaiSpec.description: Retrieves relevant chat history from your memory bank to recall specific details and enhance context awareness. This function is invoked when you need to recall details from past conversations to provide more coherent and informed responses, especially when the chat exceeds the context window. Note that user's messages are by the user and assistant's messages are yours.

userSettings.name: namespace
userSettings.label: Namespace (Recommended)
userSettings.description: The namespace where your chat is stored.

userSettings.name: topK
userSettings.label: Top K Results
userSettings.description: The number of results to return from Pinecone (default: 5).

userSettings.name: openaiEmbeddingModel
userSettings.label: OpenAI Embedding Model Name
userSettings.description: The name of the OpenAI embedding model to embed your query (e.g., text-embedding-3-small).

userSettings.name: pineconeAPIVersion
userSettings.label: Pinecone API Version
userSettings.description: The version of the Pinecone API to use (default: 2024-10).

userSettings.name: embeddingDimensions
userSettings.label: Embedding Dimensions (Optional)
userSettings.description: Specify if you want a different embedding dimension from the default. Only supported in text-embedding-3 and later models.

userSettings.name: similarityMetric
userSettings.label: Similarity Metric
userSettings.description: The similarity metric used in Pinecone. Used for relevance score calculation if rerank is disabled. Choose 'other' if unsure (default: cosine).

userSettings.name: enableRerank
userSettings.label: Enable Rerank
userSettings.description: Enable or disable Cohere Rerank for query results (default: false).

userSettings.name: cohereAPIKey
userSettings.label: Cohere API Key
userSettings.description: The API key for Cohere Rerank. Required if rerank is enabled.

userSettings.name: cohereRerankModel
userSettings.label: Cohere Rerank Model
userSettings.description: The Cohere Rerank model to use (default: rerank-v3.5).

userSettings.name: cohereTopN
userSettings.label: Cohere Top N Results
userSettings.description: The number of reranked results to return from Cohere (default: 5).

userSettings.name: cohereMaxTokensPerDoc
userSettings.label: Cohere Max Tokens Per Document
userSettings.description: The maximum number of tokens per document for Cohere Rerank (default: 4096).
